Mr. Connally received a M.B.A. from the University of Texas in 2006 and a B.A. in Economics from Vanderbilt University in 1997, where he graduated cum laude.  Prior to attending the University of Texas, he was employed by Fayez Sarofim & Co. as a Financial Analyst and co-founded Space City Sports after working at Enron Corp. as an Associate.  
