Mr. Perry received a M.B.A. from Rice University’s Jones Graduate School of Business in 2003, as well as a B.S. in Electrical & Computer Engineering and a B.A. in Mathematical Economic Analysis and Computational & Applied Mathematics from Rice University, where he graduated cum laude.  Prior to joining Fayez Sarofim & Co., he was employed with Patriot Wealth Management as a Portfolio Manager, Stanford Group Company as a Portfolio Strategist, and Petrie Parkman & Co. as an Investment Banking Analyst.

